						<summary>

						<p>Naṭarāja temple, south <hi rend="italic">gōpuram,</hi> right of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śrī-Vēṅkaṭa-dēva mahārāya Śaka 1510, Sarvadhari. Tai 22.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records that Vaiyyappa-Kṛishṇappa-Koṇḍama-nāyakkar-ayyaṉ provided for 20 meal offerings <hi rend="italic">(taḷikai)</hi> daily for God Chidambarēśvaraṉ and arranged for these 20 <hi rend="italic">taḷikai</hi> to be taken over by <hi rend="italic">sarvvakaṭṭaḷai-guru</hi> Namaśśivāya-udaiyār for distribution to itinerant mendicants <hi rend="italic">(paradēśi)</hi> (See No. 180, 193 above)</p>						

						</summary>
